The paper deals with facility location problems and proposes heuristics to solve them. This falls under the domain of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS). The problem also involves optimizing user inconvenience, which can be seen as a social impact (cs.SI) aspect. The proposed heuristics involve machine learning techniques, which can be categorized under machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the problem deals with urban scale road networks, which can be seen as a civil engineering (cs.CE) aspect.
